      <title>Details on Pope Leo XIV and his views. And, U.S. and China trade negotiations begin</title>
      <author>Brittney Melton</author>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2025/05/09/g-s1-65303/up-first-newsletter-pope-leo-us-china-trade-negotiations-medicaid</link>
