      <title>Why Israel plans to limit life-saving aid into Gaza. And, Diddy's trial begins today</title>
      <author>Brittney Melton</author>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2025/05/05/g-s1-64278/up-first-newsletter-israel-gaza-war-diddy-trial-trump-constitution</link>
