      <pubDate>Mon, 05 May 2025 10:56:53 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;div id="storytext" class="storytext storylocation linkLocation"&gt;       &lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Good morning. You're reading the Up First newsletter. &lt;/em&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.npr.org/newsletter/news" target="_blank"&gt;Subscribe&lt;/a&gt;&lt;em&gt; here to get it delivered to your inbox, and &lt;/em&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.npr.org/podcasts/510318/up-first/" target="_blank"&gt;listen&lt;/a&gt;&lt;em&gt; to the Up First podcast for all the news you need to start your day.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;   &lt;h3 class="edTag"&gt;Today's top stories&lt;/h3&gt;   &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Israel's cabinet approved a plan last night to limit the way food and supplies are distributed in Gaza&lt;/strong&gt;, saying it's the only way it will allow food back into the area. An Israeli official says it's part of a plan to take over more territory and expand the war. Main aid groups in Gaza, including the United Nations, are refusing to take part in the plan.&lt;/p&gt;   &lt;div id="resg-s1-56536-1" class="bucketwrap image large"&gt;             &lt;div     class="imagewrap has-source-dimensions"     data-crop-type=""     style="         --source-width: 8640;         --source-height: 4860;     " &gt;         &lt;picture&gt;             &lt;source srcset="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/8640x4860+0+450/resize/400/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F61%2Fb3%2F893527554196828cc110c9275153%2Fap25084398558780.jpg 400w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/8640x4860+0+450/resize/600/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F61%2Fb3%2F893527554196828cc110c9275153%2Fap25084398558780.jpg 600w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/8640x4860+0+450/resize/800/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F61%2Fb3%2F893527554196828cc110c9275153%2Fap25084398558780.jpg 800w, https://npr.brightspotcdn