      <title>Trump administration tries to ramp up deportations. And, a look at Canada's election</title>
      <author>Brittney Melton</author>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2025/04/28/g-s1-63084/up-first-newsletter-trump-mass-deportations-measles-canada-elections</link>
      <comments>https://text.npr.org/2025/04/28/g-s1-63084/up-first-newsletter-trump-mass-deportations-measles-canada-elections</comments>
      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.npr.org/2025/04/28/g-s1-63084/up-first-newsletter-trump-mass-deportations-measles-canada-elections</guid>
